on as executive chairman which gives him unique insights into our challenges opportunities and operations and his strong background of senior management and executive experience in the mobile gaming and content sectors led the board to conclude that he should serve as a director source glu mobile inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view niccolo m de masis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like niccolo m de masi more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in niccolo m de masis network and community follow changes in niccolo m de masis employment and moneyinmotion connect with niccolo m de masi through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example niccolo m de masi niccolo m de masis connections  sign up now to view niccolo m de masis  connections » ellen f siminoff board member zynga inc a brooke seawell board member nvidia corporation ann mather board member alphabet inc susan d bowick former board member earthlink holdings corp hany m nada former board member glu mobile inc eric r ludwig chief operating officer executive vice president and chief financial officer glu mobile inc adam flanders former senior vice president business development and communications glu mobile inc thomas m perrault former vp global human resources glu mobile inc william j miller board member waters corporation kevin s chou former vice president general counsel and secretary glu mobile inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla michael c montgomery board member nmi holdings inc × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature i